# Privacy Policy for WhatsApp Media Finder

**Last Updated: [17th November 2025]**

## Introduction
WhatsApp Media Finder ("we", "our", or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your data when you use our mobile application.

## Data Collection and Usage

### Local Data Storage
- Our app accesses your WhatsApp media files (images, videos, audio, documents) stored on your device
- We extract text from images and documents using OCR (Optical Character Recognition) technology
- We calculate file hashes to identify duplicate files
- All data is stored locally on your device in a SQLite database
- We do not transmit, upload, or share any of your data with external servers or third parties

### Permissions Required
Our app requires the following permissions to function:
- **Storage/Media Access**: To read WhatsApp media files from your device
- **Photos, Videos, Audio**: To access and organize your media files
- **Manage External Storage**: To access files across your device storage

### Data Processing
- **OCR Processing**: Text extraction from images and documents is performed entirely on your device
- **Duplicate Detection**: File hash calculations are performed locally
- **No Cloud Services**: All processing happens on your device - no data leaves your device

## Data Sharing
We do not share, sell, or transmit any of your data to third parties, external servers, or cloud services. All data remains on your device.

## Data Security
- All data is stored locally in an encrypted SQLite database
- No network connections are made to external servers
- Your files are never uploaded or transmitted

## Age Restrictions
Our app is available to users of all ages. We do not collect personal information from anyone, including children, as all data remains on your device.

## Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by updating the "Last Updated" date.

## Contact Us
